{"tid":1087283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟打錯電話既人講聲sorry有幾難？","createTime":"2019-04-01T09:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T10:55:48.000Z","uid":199757,"like":31,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0af9ca728f95975506826b571ee7236fe11c7b3c","tid":1087283,"uid":199757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T09:08:32.000Z","msg":"岩岩上緊堂 有個3字頭既電話打過黎 我以為係有咩通知我就聽左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一聽 佢冇出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我喂左幾下 佢都冇應<br />\n過左幾秒 佢用好似同隔離既人講既語氣同聲線講左句<br />\n<strong>打錯電話喎</strong> <br />\n然後一野cut左我線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3字頭2字頭好多人都唔聽 我係驚miss左d咩緊要嘅通知先聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打錯電話一野cut人地線係好爽係唔洗諗咁多野唔洗講咁多野<br />\n但聽嗰個真係好不爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似有個死mk一野撞埋黎仲笑騎騎走左去<br />\n<br />\nSorry打錯都係一句姐 但起碼會令人舒服好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 毒撚 唔識打電話去屌番佢 淨係識上連登出po發洩"},{"pid":"b027f795d2642d55cdac8b3623bff4948292a754","tid":1087283,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T09:10:50.000Z","msg":"我當初同你一樣太好人 成日俾人com線<br />\n依家一句打錯就cut鳩佢線 無痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68a0f241d470734e930c38c35545fb413b087c4","tid":1087283,"uid":199757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b027f795d2642d55cdac8b3623bff4948292a754","tid":1087283,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T09:10:50.000Z","msg":"我當初同你一樣太好人 成日俾人com線<br />\n依家一句打錯就cut鳩佢線 無痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T09:12:56.000Z","msg":"手速唔夠快 cut唔反佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02b3edbf22d2263ae57333a52b6ec5e78d56636","tid":1087283,"uid":71428,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"p